entities.json
graphify-out/
VERIFICATION-REPORT.md
*.local.md
vendor/*.tar.gz
vendor/*.zip
vendor/codebase-memory-mcp

# benchmark 报告（生成产物，默认不入库；正经 benchmark 跑完手动 git add 归档）
eval/reports/
